# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md
msgid "Above ground biomass"
msgstr "Biomasa sobre el suelo"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:17
msgid ""
"The biomass of living vegetation, both woody and herbaceous, above the soil "
"including stems, stumps, branches, bark, seeds, and foliage"
msgstr ""
"La biomasa de la vegetación viva, tanto leñosa como herbácea, por encima del"
" suelo, incluidos tallos, tocones, ramas, corteza, semillas y follaje."

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:19
#, python-brace-format
