# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:5
msgid "Adaptation"
msgstr "Adaptación"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:22
msgid ""
"The process of adjustment to actual or expected climate and its effects. In "
"human systems, adaptation seeks to moderate or avoid harm or exploit "
"beneficial opportunities. In some natural systems, human intervention may "
"facilitate adjustment to expected climate and its effects."
msgstr ""
"El proceso de ajuste al clima real o previsto y a sus efectos. En los "
"sistemas humanos, la adaptación busca moderar o evitar los daños o "
"aprovechar las oportunidades beneficiosas. En algunos sistemas naturales, la"
" intervención humana puede facilitar el ajuste al clima previsto y a sus "
"efectos."

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:8
msgid "Administrative unit"
msgstr "Unidad administrativa"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:25
msgid ""
"A geographic area that serves administrative and governmental functions. "
"They are usually defined and established by legal action."
msgstr ""
"Área geográfica que cumple funciones administrativas y gubernamentales. "
"Suelen definirse y establecerse por vía legal."

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:11
msgid "Affected Area"
msgstr "Zona afectada"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:28
msgid ""
"An arid, semi-arid and/or dry sub-humid area affected or threatened by "
"desertification"
msgstr ""
"Una zona árida, semiárida y/o subhúmeda seca afectada o amenazada por la "
"desertificación"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:14
msgid "Afforestation"
msgstr "Forestación"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:31
msgid ""
"Afforestation is planting of new forests on lands that historically have not"
" contained forests."
msgstr ""
"La forestación es la plantación de nuevos bosques en tierras que "
"históricamente no han contenido bosques."

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:17
msgid "Aggregation"
msgstr "Agregación"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:34
msgid ""
"The combination of related categories, usually within a common branch of a "
"hierarchy, to provide information at a broader level to that at which "
"detailed observations are taken."
msgstr ""
"La combinación de categorías relacionadas, normalmente dentro de una rama "
"común de una jerarquía, para proporcionar información a un nivel más amplio "
"que aquel en el que se toman las observaciones detalladas."

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:20
#, python-format
msgid "Agriculture, value added (% of gross domestic product)"
msgstr "Agricultura, valor añadido (% del producto interior bruto)"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:37
msgid ""
"One of the factors recommended to estimate the economic component of the "
"Drought Vulnerability Index (DVI). Agriculture corresponds to International "
"Standard Industrial Classifications (ISIC) divisions 1-5 and includes "
"forestry, hunting, and fishing, as well as cultivation of crops and "
"livestock production. This factor refers to the value added for agriculture "
"as a percentage of the gross value added at factor cost. It implies a higher"
" coping capacity of populations."
msgstr ""
"Es uno de los factores recomendados para estimar el componente económico del"
" Índice de Vulnerabilidad a la Sequía (IVS). La agricultura corresponde a "
"las divisiones 1-5 de la Clasificación Industrial Internacional Uniforme "
"(CIIU) e incluye la silvicultura, la caza y la pesca, así como los cultivos "
"y la producción ganadera. Este factor se refiere al valor añadido de la "
"agricultura como porcentaje del valor añadido bruto al coste de los "
"factores. Implica una mayor capacidad de adaptación de las poblaciones."

